{"about_the_game":"Itsy is a heart tug the length of a bus ride.  A narrative endless climber Inspired by the struggles with &amp; healing from Autism-burnout.  Itsy is a &quot;Micro-A&quot; title, you can play for story (progress autosaves), or endlessly &amp; conquer the leaderboard.   Story can be toggled on and off. Dual leaderboards means you can try to top the scoreboards in distance or Sky-Raisins. Or can you do both?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou ever feel down?  By something that seemed to go on forever?  No end in sight?   That's how the Itsy Bitsy Spider feels, endlessly making his way up the waterspout against all the rain water that washes him away.   When it's the 876,240 time to try again - how does he keep going?   How do YOU keep going?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- Autosave- Can be toggled on and off.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 2 Play Modes! -<br />\r\n    --Story Mode-- Play for story!  (Can Autosave and both Dialogue &amp; Visibility Progress!)<br />\r\n                         OR<br />\r\n    --Endless Mode-- Play Classic Endless Mode! (No Autosave, No Dialogue, No Visibility Progression)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Accessibility -<br />\r\n    -- Red-Green colour blindness mode --<br />\r\n    -- &quot;hold-down-click&quot; instead of &quot;rapid-clicking&quot; when swimming --<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Leaderboards -<br />\r\n    -- Distance Score Board<br />\r\n    -- Sky-Raisin Point Score Board","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hungry Spider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2960480/01422405fc688e11c7bc7496d5d2460e0e6e24e1.jpg"},{"name":"Hungry Hungry Spider ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2960480/c45443731c1f5a74bba9444f696e9cca30d8df5c.jpg"},{"name":"Extra Hungry Spider ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2960480/b5d88f8fa0f301e4678aa5521fd566cf610660c9.jpg"},{"name":"A Most Hungry  Spider","path":"https://cdn.akam